 'Feet landing out of balance; pressing out instead of pushing under; dip too deep reducing leg drive effectiveness; catching with bent elbows.',
 'overhead_strength', array['Two feet land at the same time','Lock the arms before you land: no pressing out','Your legs drive it up, your body drops under','Shoulder-width catch: wide enough for balance, not too wide'],
