 'Simulate a competition session. Snatch: 6 attempts in order, increasing weight. Clean & Jerk: 6 attempts. Rest: 3 minutes between each attempt (as in competition). Warm-up protocol: specific warm-up to opener weight. Decide openers at 90-92% of max. Competition mindset: treat each lift as a competition attempt. Record: make/miss on each attempt for pattern analysis.',
 'Openers too heavy (should be a sure make); not allowing full 3-minute rest between attempts; changing technique under competition pressure; no warm-up protocol simulation.',
