 'HYROX-style three-machine conditioning circuit. 500m ski erg, immediately 500m row, immediately 2-minute max calories assault bike. Rest 3 minutes. Repeat 3-4 rounds. The transitions test the ability to change muscle groups under cardiovascular fatigue. Record total calories on the bike as the score for each round — it drops as fatigue accumulates across the triplet.',
 'Starting the ski erg too hard and arriving at the row destroyed; poor technique on the row when fatigued (back rounding); not maintaining power on the bike despite leg fatigue from the row.',
