 'Burpee below a pull-up bar. Drop to chest-to-floor burpee directly under the bar. Jump up, grip the bar, perform 1 pull-up (chin over bar). Lower, release, land, burpee immediately. Continuous movement. The combination of pushing, pulling, and hip extension makes this a complete upper body conditioning movement. Scale: jumping pull-up instead of strict.',
