('Kettlebell Swing to Squat Combination',
 'glutes', array['quads','core','hamstrings'], array['glutes','quads','core'],
 'strength', 'explosive', array['kettlebell'], 'intermediate', true,
 'Kettlebell swing combined with a squat. Perform 5 swings, on the 5th swing catch the bell in a goblet hold at chest height, perform a full squat, stand, then swing the bell back into the next sequence. Or: dead squat on the downswing — squat as the bell swings back between the legs, use the squat to add to the hip drive on the next swing. Both variations are used for conditioning and power development.',
