 'Body held horizontal sideways on a vertical pole. Both hands grip the pole: top hand pushes (tricep/shoulder), bottom hand pulls (lat/bicep). The body is held parallel to the ground through sheer core lateral flexion and shoulder force couple. Progressions: tuck flag → straddle flag → full flag. Training approach: side planks, lateral core work, and the push-pull on the pole specifically.',
