 'Foundation calisthenics program. A: Dead hang (3x20-30s — builds grip and shoulder decompression). B: Band-assisted pull-up 3x8. C: Push-up 3x10-15 (chest to floor, arms at 45°). D: Air squat 3x15. E: Plank 3x30s. F: Inverted row (TRX or bar at waist height) 3x10. G: Hollow body hold 3x15s. Progress: remove band, add deficit push-up, add Bulgarian split squat, extend hold times.',
